* op_dispatch.sno
* Bottleneck: operator dispatch (string dict lookup per arithmetic op)
* All four arithmetic ops + comparison in rotation. Expected: ~9000000
        N = 1
        OUTER = 0
OUTER   N = N + 3
        N = N - 1
        N = N * 2
        N = GE(N, 10000000) N / 10000  :S(OUTER)F(NEXT)
NEXT    OUTER = LT(OUTER, 100000) OUTER + 1  :S(OUTER)
        OUTPUT = N
end
